OL,6,FPolice, campaigners and the Stormont
OL,7,FExecutive are calling for the public
OL,8,Fto be extra vigilant when using the
OL,9,Froads.
OL,11,FIt comes after figures show that 68
OL,12,Fpeople were killed in road tragedies
OL,13,Fin 2024. With a total of nine lives
OL,14,Fclaimed in December alone.
OL,16,FDavy Jackson from the charity Road
OL,17,FSafe NI said: "That is 68 families who
OL,18,Fhave lost loved ones. Families that
OL,19,Fwill never be the same again.
