OL,6,F"If everyone would avoid those, there
OL,7,Fwould be a lot less collisions on our
OL,8,Froads. I would ask everyone to be
OL,9,Fcareful whether they are walking,
OL,10,Fcycling or driving.
OL,12,F"Whatever you are doing, take
OL,13,Fresponsibility for your own road
OL,14,Fsafety and the safety of others around
OL,15,Fyou", Mr Jackson said.
OL,17,FThe police have said that there has
OL,18,Fbeen an increase in elderly victims
OL,19,Fand that more crashes are happening in
OL,20,Frural areas.
