OL,4,Cabout road safety
OL,6,FInspector Cherith Adair, from the
OL,7,FCollision Investigation Unit, said:
OL,8,F"Traditionally, we would have seen a
OL,9,Flot of fatals and road traffic
OL,10,Fcollisions involving younger or more
OL,11,Finexperienced drivers.
OL,13,F"This year we are seeing the same
OL,14,Fcollisions involving elderly drivers
OL,15,Fand very elderly drivers that we would
OL,16,Fnot have seen in previous years.
OL,18,F"The border corridor would be where we
OL,19,Fsee a lot of fatalities. A lot of
OL,20,Frural collisions, very serious
OL,21,Finjuries, as well as fatalities.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
