OL,6,F"Not so much in an urban environment,
OL,7,Fwhich you may expect with the volume
OL,8,Fof traffic in our cities.
OL,10,F"Our statistics would show more of a
OL,11,Frural driving problem."
OL,13,FThe PSNI stressed that behind every
OL,14,Ffigure and every fatality is a family
OL,15,Fleft devastated.
OL,17,F"Every single one of these fatalities
OL,18,Fleaves a family devastated by a
OL,19,Fshocking and unexpected death.
