OL,3,CPublic urged to spread the message
OL,4,Cabout road safety
OL,6,F"Unless it happens to you I do not
OL,7,Fthink that anyone can understand the
OL,8,Fdevastation of that," Inspector Adair
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FIn his annual road safety report,
OL,12,FInfrastructure John O'Dowd expressed
OL,13,Fhis condolences to the families of
OL,14,Fthose who died on Northern Ireland's
OL,15,Froads in 2024.
OL,17,FThe Minister for Infrastructure
OL,18,Fencouraged the public to spread road
OL,19,Fsafety messaging and talk about road
OL,20,Fsafety with family and friends in the
OL,21,Fhope that 2025 will be a better year.
