OL,3,CPublic urged to spread the message
OL,4,Cabout road safety
OL,6,F"As 2025 begins, I appeal to everyone
OL,7,Fto think about your behaviour when
OL,8,Fusing the roads. Make a potentially
OL,9,Flifesaving choice to be more mindful
OL,10,Fof others and proceed with care,
OL,11,Ffollow the rules of the road ` they
OL,12,Fare there to protect us and help
OL,13,Feveryone get home safe.
OL,15,F"As we start a new year, the harsh
OL,16,Ftruth is that we all need to wise up
OL,17,Fwhen we are using our roads because if
OL,18,Fwe don't the number of deaths will
OL,19,Fcontinue to rise."
